===== Install
- Download [Winless](http://winless.org/), install it and run it
- Click "Add folder" and select your less folder (for example /app/sawhat/public/less)
- Select files to compile ("_[name].less" files shouldn't be selected)
- Click the "Minify" checkbox
- Go to File > Settings and check "Automatically compile files when saved"
- Other options are up to you